                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Overall Conversion Rate: 11.27%</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Cellular contact performs better than telephone.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Previous successful campaigns achieve the highest conversion.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Students and retired customers show stronger conversion rates.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• March and December are the best-performing months.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>Recommendations</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Focus on cellular outreach.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Retarget previously converted customers.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Prioritize high-converting customer segments.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true'>• Increase campaigns during peak months.</run>
